      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. This example retains its mechanical purity with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles high-lateral G-loads with precision. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the original McPherson strut/multi-link geometry for optimal kinematics. A mechanically sound specimen with a clean power band, ready for the apex.",
