      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and reliability. Meticulously maintained and showing only the expected signs of careful use, this automobile offers a refined driving experience and a well-preserved aesthetic. It represents a superior choice for the professional seeking an authoritative presence on the road coupled with mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 36800.0,
