    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable ride for someone who wants quality without the 'brand-new' price tag. It runs beautifully and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Drop me a message if you\u2019d like to come see it and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
