    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically sound; the high-pressure VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain structural rigidity. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a limited-slip variable M differential for optimal power delivery during cornering. While the body shows honest patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains a benchmark of naturally aspirated performance. This is a well-sorted machine for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity and tactile feedback.",
